#. Tag: title
#: contenteditor.docbook:1
#, no-c-format
msgid "Portfolio Content"
msgstr "Vsebina portfelja"

#. Tag: chapter
#: contenteditor.docbook:1
#, no-c-format
msgid "&WORK-IN-PROGRESS;"
msgstr "&WORK-IN-PROGRESS;"

#. Tag: para
#: contenteditor.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "This editor enables you to configure the content of your portfolio."
msgstr ""
"Ta urejevalnik vam omogoča, da konfigurirate vsebino svojega portfelja."

#. Tag: para
#: contenteditor.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>Insert</keycap></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or press "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> to add projects to your portfolio."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>Vstavi</keycap></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ali "
"pritisnite <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> za dodajte projekte v svoj portfelj."

#. Tag: para
#: contenteditor.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>Delete</keycap></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or "
"press <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> to remove selected projects."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>Delete</keycap></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odstrani</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"ali pritisnite <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton> za odstranitev izbranih "
"projektov."

#. Tag: para
#: contenteditor.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the projects you are managing and set <guilabel>Portfolio</guilabel> = "
"<emphasis>Yes</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte projekte, ki jih upravljate, in nastavite <guilabel>Portfelj</"
"guilabel> = <emphasis>Da</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: contenteditor.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have resources that is used by projects not part of your portfolio "
"and you want to re-schedule or inspect resource usage, you need to add all "
"relevant projects and set <guilabel>Portfolio</guilabel> = <emphasis>No</"
"emphasis> for these projects."
msgstr ""
"Če imate vire, ki jih uporabljajo projekti, ki niso del vašega portfelja, in "
"želite znova razporediti ali pregledati uporabo virov, morate dodati vse "
"ustrezne projekte in nastaviti <guilabel>Portfelj</guilabel> = <emphasis>Ne</"
"emphasis> za te projekte."

#. Tag: title
#: contenteditor.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "Storage"
msgstr "Hramba"

#. Tag: para
#: contenteditor.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Project changes can be saved to the original project file or it can be "
"embedded into the portfolio file. If you are managing projects, they should "
"normally be saved to their original files. Set <guilabel>Store</guilabel> = "
"<emphasis>External</emphasis> in this case. However, if you just want to see "
"what impact changes might have, you may want to store projects embedded "
"while you are working on different scenarios. Set <guilabel>Store</guilabel> "
"= <emphasis>Embedded</emphasis> in this case. The projects external url is "
"preserved if you later want to save the changes to the original file."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe projekta je mogoče shraniti v izvirno datoteko projekta ali pa jih "
"je mogoče vdelati v datoteko portfelja. Če upravljate projekte, jih je treba "
"običajno shraniti v izvirne datoteke. V tem primeru nastavite "
"<guilabel>Hramba</guilabel> = <emphasis>Zunanja</emphasis>. Če pa želite "
"samo videti, kakšen vpliv bi lahko imele spremembe, boste morda želeli "
"shraniti vdelane projekte, medtem ko delate na različnih scenarijih. V tem "
"primeru nastavite <guilabel>Hramba</guilabel> = <emphasis>Vdelana</"
"emphasis>. Zunanji url projekta se ohrani, če pozneje želite shraniti "
"spremembe v izvirno datoteko."
